Package Models

Class AggressivePlayer

java.lang.Object
Models.PlayerBehavior
Models.AggressivePlayer
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class AggressivePlayer extends PlayerBehavior
This is the class of an Aggressive Player. An Aggressive player, gathers all his armies, attacks from his strongest territory and deploys armies to maximize his forces on one country.
